# Optional: self-hosted dictionary proxy (Cloudflare Worker).
#
# The published website (GitHub Pages) can't reach Jisho.org directly because
# Jisho sends no CORS headers. Deploy the Worker in worker/ and put its URL here
# so the production build prefers it over flaky public proxies.
#
# For GitHub Pages, copy this into a committed `.env.production` (the URL is not
# secret — it's a public endpoint). Vite loads it automatically at build time.
#
# Native apps (Capacitor) and local dev (Vite proxy) do NOT need this.
VITE_DICT_PROXY=https://jlpt-dict-proxy.YOUR-SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
